@Node Main "Internal Changes to HydraBBS between V1.02 and V1.07"

  *** Developer Information ***

  This document is stored as:

    HBBS:Developer/Docs/Upgrades/Dev_Changes_V1.07.guide


  If you have written some doors or are going to write some, then please
  read the following information:


  Internal Changes to HydraBBS between V1.02 and V1.07
  ====================================================

  * HBBSCommon.library and HBBSNode.library

    There is now full documentation in autodoc format, which can be displayed
    in your favorite text viewer or autodoc viewer as well as amigaguide
    versions.

    Please see the following files:

    HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSCommon.library.doc
    HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSNode.library.doc

    @{"HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSCommon.library.guide" link HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSCommon.library.guide/MAIN}
    @{"HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSNode.library.guide" link HBBS:Developer/Docs/HBBSNode.library.guide/MAIN}

  * Also, for a limited period, you can get the source code for free if you
    are going to write some doors, please see the @{"web-site" link HBBS:HBBS.Guide/Website} or @{"e-mail" link HBBS:HBBS.Guide/email} me
    for details.

@EndNode

